se are exactly what keep the stock suppressed.\n\n## What has to be true for $27.50\n\nThe stock realistically reaches $27.50 when the market believes R2 will ship at volume with improving margins — i.e., the \"will Rivian survive and scale?\" question flips to \"how fast does Rivian grow?\" That's typically a **multi-quarter re-rating tied to R2 proof points**, not a news-day pop. Absent a buyout or a blowout catalyst, this is more plausibly a **2026–2027 story than a \"next few weeks\" one** — but that's a framework, not a forecast, and it's anchored to stale data.\n\n## To get you a real answer, pick one:\n\n1. **Grant web access** (approve the WebSearch/WebFetch prompt) and I'll pull the live price, current analyst target range, R2 timeline updates, and latest cash position — then give you a data-grounded scenario analysis (bear/base/bull with rough timeframes and the catalysts to watch).\n2. **Tell me today's RIVN price** and I'll build the analysis around it immediately.\n\nWant me to proceed once web access is on? That's the version actually worth acting on.\n\n*Not financial advice — I'm an analysis tool, not a licensed advisor. Position sizing and your own risk tolerance matter more than any target.*","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"5ba2aae4-033b-5a4e-b487-3cd41d131f60","total_cost_usd":0.169693,"usage":{"input_tokens":8,"cache_creation_input_tokens":6419,"cache_read_input_tokens":102020,"output_tokens":2153,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":6419,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"not_available","iterations":[{"input_tokens":2,"output_tokens":1370,"cache_read_input_tokens":27382,"cache_creation_input_tokens":442,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":442},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001":{"inputTokens":548,"outputTokens":16,"cacheReadInputTokens":0,"c